OL,3,CIrvine Welsh says hosting event
OL,4,Ccelebrating late Pam Hogg is 'real
OL,5,Cprivilege'
OL,7,FIrvine Welsh has said it is a "real
OL,8,Fprivilege" to be taking part in an
OL,9,Fevent celebrating the legacy of his
OL,10,Ffriend, the late fashion designer Pam
OL,11,FHogg, in her home town.
OL,13,FThe designer, known for her bold and
OL,14,Feccentric style, died in November last
OL,15,Fyear at St Joseph's Hospice in
OL,16,FHackney, London.
OL,26,@oD@_OUpD@JO]
