OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774054967
OL,3,CIrvine Welsh says hosting event
OL,4,Ccelebrating late Pam Hogg is 'real
OL,5,Cprivilege'
OL,7,FBorn in Paisley in Renfrewshire, she
OL,8,Fstudied fine art and printed textiles
OL,9,Fat the Glasgow School of Art before
OL,10,Fattending the Royal College of Art in
OL,11,FLondon.
OL,13,FShe went on to forge a career that saw
OL,14,Fher create looks for the likes of
OL,15,FRihanna, Kate Moss, Lady Gaga, Kylie
OL,16,FMinogue and Beyonce.
OL,18,FTrainspotting author Welsh will host
OL,19,Fan event celebrating her life and
OL,20,Flegacy on Friday March 27 as part of
OL,21,Fthe first Paisley Arts Festival.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774054967
OL,3,CIrvine Welsh says hosting event
OL,4,Ccelebrating late Pam Hogg is 'real
OL,5,Cprivilege'
OL,7,FHe said: "It's a real privilege to be
OL,8,Fpart of something where it's her home
OL,9,Fturf, it's a great thing."
OL,11,FWelsh said the designer's impact
OL,12,Fextended beyond fashion and that she
OL,13,Fmay be remembered as an "artist of the
OL,14,Fbody".
OL,16,FHe said: "She didn't make stuff for
OL,17,Fthe mass market, she didn't make high
OL,18,Fstreet fashion.
OL,26,@oD@JOUqD@ZO]uD@YOUvD@EO]xD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774054967
OL,3,CIrvine Welsh says hosting event
OL,4,Ccelebrating late Pam Hogg is 'real
OL,5,Cprivilege'
OL,7,F"She made things that would be
OL,8,Fspectacular and shocking and didn't
OL,9,Flike the watering down of that.
OL,11,F"I think the fashion aspect may become
OL,12,Fless prominent and she'll be seen as
OL,13,Fan artist of the body who created this
OL,14,Famazing work.
OL,16,F"She's a 3D artist and a major British
OL,17,Fartist. That'll be her legacy."
OL,19,FWelsh first met Hogg in London's Soho
OL,20,Fin the 1980s and they were close
OL,21,Ffriends for decades.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOUyD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
