SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774054967
OL,3,CIrvine Welsh says hosting event
OL,4,Ccelebrating late Pam Hogg is 'real
OL,5,Cprivilege'
OL,7,FHe spoke of the lasting impression she
OL,8,Fmade on those she met and her ability
OL,9,Fto connect with people from different
OL,10,Ffields.
OL,12,FWelsh said: "She was an ubiquitous
OL,13,Fperson, would just show up everywhere.
OL,15,F"She'd talk to everyone in a room and
OL,16,Fmade you feel like the important
OL,17,Fperson, and there's few people that
OL,18,Fcan do that ` it's a real gift."
OL,26,@tD@MOUwD@AOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
