OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774054967
OL,3,CIrvine Welsh says hosting event
OL,4,Ccelebrating late Pam Hogg is 'real
OL,5,Cprivilege'
OL,7,FWelsh will be joined on the panel at
OL,8,Fthe event by Scottish model and
OL,9,Factress Eunice Olumide, and fashion
OL,10,Fhistorian and curator Mairi MacKenzie.
OL,11,FThey will share their perspectives on
OL,12,FHogg's enduring cultural impact.
OL,14,FPam Hogg: Style, Defiance And The Art
OL,15,FOf Being Seen will take place at
OL,16,FPaisley Town Hall at 8.30pm on March
OL,17,F27.
OL,19,FThe Paisley Arts Festival runs from
OL,20,FMarch 27 to 29.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
